quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"qal lah qwmh: kayf nsddiqk wntbek, waladhin atabaeuk aradhl alnaas wasaflhm?"
  26,112,"fajabhm nuh ealayh alslam bqwlh: last mklfana bmerft aemalhm, 'iinama kulft 'ana adewhm 'iilaa al'iyman. walaetbar bial'iiman la balhsb walnsb walhirf walsnaye"
  26,113,ma hisabuhum lljza' ealaa 'aemalihim wbwatnhm 'iilaa ealaa rabiy almttalie ealaa alsrayr. law kuntum tasheurun bdhlk lamaa qultum hdha alklam
  26,114,"wma 'ana bitarid aladhin yuminun bdewty, mahma takun halhm; talbiat lrghbtkm kay tuminuu by. ma 'ana 'iilaa nadhir byin al'indhar"
  26,115,"wma 'ana bitarid aladhin yuminun bdewty, mahma takun halhm; talbiat lrghbtkm kay tuminuu by. ma 'ana 'iilaa nadhir byin al'indhar"
  26,116,"edl qawm nuh ean almhawrt 'iilaa althdyd, faqaluu lh: layin lam trje- ya nwh- ean daewatak ltkwnnn min almqtwlyn rmyana balhjart"
  26,117,"flma sumie nuh qawlihim hdha daea rabah bqwlh: rabi 'iina qawmi 'asaruu ealaa tkdhyby, fahkum bayni wabaynahum hkmana tuhlk bih man jhd twhydk wkdhdhab rswlk, wanajini wman maei min almuminin mimaa tueadhib bih alkafryn"
  26,118,"flma sumie nuh qawlihim hdha daea rabah bqwlh: rabi 'iina qawmi 'asaruu ealaa tkdhyby, fahkum bayni wabaynahum hkmana tuhlk bih man jhd twhydk wkdhdhab rswlk, wanajini wman maei min almuminin mimaa tueadhib bih alkafryn"
  26,119,fanjynah wman maeah fi alsafinat almmlw't bsnwf almkhlwqat alty hamalaha meh
  26,120,"thm 'aghraqna baed 'inja' nuh waman maeah albaqyn, aladhin lam yuminuu min qawmih wrddu ealayh alnsyht"
  26,121,"'in fi naba nuh wama kan min 'inja' almuminin w'ihlak almukadhibin laelamt webrtan ezymt liman bedhm, wama kan 'akthar aladhin samieuu hadhih alqisat muminin biallah wabirasulih wshreh"
  26,122,"w'in rabak lahu aleaziz fi antqamh mmn kafar bih wakhalaf amrh, alrahim bieibadih almwmnyn"
  26,123,kdhdhabt qbylt ead rasuluhum hwdana- ealayh alslam- fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsl; liaitihad daeawtuhum fi 'usuliha wghaytha
  26,124,"'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum hwd: 'alaa takhshawn allah ftkhlsu lah alebad? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum lhdaytkm w'irshadkm, hafiz ealaa risalatan allh, abllighha lakum kama amrny rby, fkhafu eiqab allah watyewny fima jitukum bih min eind allh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa 'irshadkm 'iilaa altwhyd ay nawe min 'anwae alajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,125,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum hwd: 'alaa takhshawn allah ftkhlsu lah alebad? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum lhdaytkm w'irshadkm, hafiz ealaa risalatan allh, abllighha lakum kama amrny rby, fkhafu eiqab allah watyewny fima jitukum bih min eind allh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa 'irshadkm 'iilaa altwhyd ay nawe min 'anwae alajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,126,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum hwd: 'alaa takhshawn allah ftkhlsu lah alebad? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum lhdaytkm w'irshadkm, hafiz ealaa risalatan allh, abllighha lakum kama amrny rby, fkhafu eiqab allah watyewny fima jitukum bih min eind allh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa 'irshadkm 'iilaa altwhyd ay nawe min 'anwae alajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,127,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum hwd: 'alaa takhshawn allah ftkhlsu lah alebad? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum lhdaytkm w'irshadkm, hafiz ealaa risalatan allh, abllighha lakum kama amrny rby, fkhafu eiqab allah watyewny fima jitukum bih min eind allh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa 'irshadkm 'iilaa altwhyd ay nawe min 'anwae alajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,128,"atbnwn bikuli makan murtafie bina' ealyana tshrfwn minh ftskhrwn min almar? wdhlk ebth w'israf la yaeud ealaykum bfaydt fi aldiyn 'aw aldnya, watatakhidhun qswrana mnyet whswnana mshyadt, kankm takhludun fi aldunya wala tmwtwn, wa'iidha batashtum bahd min alkhalq qutila 'aw drbana, faealtum dhlk qahryn zalmyn"
  26,129,"'atabnun bikuli makan murtafie bina' ealyana tshrfwn minh ftskhrwn min almar? wdhlk ebth w'israf la yaeud ealaykum bfaydt fi aldiyn 'aw aldnya, watatakhidhun qswrana mnyet whswnana mshyadt, kankm takhludun fi aldunya wala tmwtwn, wa'iidha batashtum bahd min alkhalq qutila 'aw drbana, faealtum dhlk qahryn zalmyn"
  26,130,"atbnwn bikuli makan murtafie bina' ealyana tshrfwn minh ftskhrwn min almar? wdhlk ebth w'israf la yaeud ealaykum bfaydt fi aldiyn 'aw aldnya, watatakhidhun qswrana mnyet whswnana mshyadt, kankm takhludun fi aldunya wala tmwtwn, wa'iidha batashtum bahd min alkhalq qutila 'aw drbana, faealtum dhlk qahryn zalmyn"
  26,131,"fkhafu allh, wamtthlu ma 'adeukum 'iilayh fa'iinah anfe lkm, wakhshawa allah aladhi aetakm min 'anwae alnaeam ma la khfa' fih elykm, aetakm alaneam: min al'iibil walbqr walghnm, waetakm alawlad, waetakm albsatyn almthmrt, wfjjar lakum alma' min aleuyun aljaryt"
  26,132,"fkhafu allh, wamtthlu ma 'adeukum 'iilayh fa'iinah anfe lkm, wakhshawa allah aladhi aetakm min 'anwae alnaeam ma la khfa' fih elykm, aetakm alaneam: min al'iibil walbqr walghnm, waetakm alawlad, waetakm albsatyn almthmrt, wfjjar lakum alma' min aleuyun aljaryt"
  26,133,"fkhafu allh, wamtthlu ma 'adeukum 'iilayh fa'iinah anfe lkm, wakhshawa allah aladhi aetakm min 'anwae alnaeam ma la khfa' fih elykm, aetakm alaneam: min al'iibil walbqr walghnm, waetakm alawlad, waetakm albsatyn almthmrt, wfjjar lakum alma' min aleuyun aljaryt"
  26,134,"fkhafu allh, wamtthlu ma 'adeukum 'iilayh fa'iinah anfe lkm, wakhshawa allah aladhi aetakm min 'anwae alnaeam ma la khfa' fih elykm, aetakm alaneam: min al'iibil walbqr walghnm, waetakm alawlad, waetakm albsatyn almthmrt, wfjjar lakum alma' min aleuyun aljaryt"
  26,135,"qal hwd- ealayh alssalam- mhdhrana lhm: 'iiniy 'akhaf 'iin asrrtm ealaa ma 'antum ealayh min altkdhyb walzlm wkufr alnniem, 'an yunazil allah bikum edhabana fi yawm tezm shdth min hwl edhabh"
  26,136,"qalu lh: yastawi eindana tdhkyrk wtkhwyfk lana wtrkh, falan numin lk"
  26,137,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy nahn ealayh 'iilaa din al'awalin weadathm, wama nahn bimueadhabin ealaa ma nafeal mimaa hadhdhartna minh min aledhab"
  26,138,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy nahn ealayh 'iilaa din al'awalin weadathm, wama nahn bimueadhabin ealaa ma nafeal mimaa hadhdhartna minh min aledhab"
  26,139,"fastmarru ealaa tkdhybh, fahlkhm allah birih bardt shdyd. 'iina fi dhalik al'ihlak laebrt liman bedhm, wama kan 'akthar aladhin samieuu qsthm muminin bk. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz alghalb ealaa ma yuriduh min 'ihlak almkdhbyn, alrahim balmwmnyn"
  26,140,"fastmarru ealaa tkdhybh, fahlkhm allah birih bardt shdyd. 'iina fi dhalik al'ihlak laebrt liman bedhm, wama kan 'akthar aladhin samieuu qsthm muminin bk. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz alghalb ealaa ma yuriduh min 'ihlak almkdhbyn, alrahim balmwmnyn"
  26,141,"kdhdhabt qbylt thamud 'akhahum salhana fi risalatih wdewth 'iilaa tawhid allh, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsl; li'anahum jmyeana yadeun 'iilaa tawhid allh"
  26,142,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum salh: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allh, ftufridwnh balebad? 'iiniy mrsal min allah 'ilykm, hafiz ealaa hadhih alrisalat kama tlqytha ean allh, fahdharuu eqabh teala, wamtthlu ma daeawtukum 'ilyh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa nushi w'irshady lakum 'aya jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,143,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum salh: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allh, ftufridwnh balebad? 'iiniy mrsal min allah 'ilykm, hafiz ealaa hadhih alrisalat kama tlqytha ean allh, fahdharuu eqabh teala, wamtthlu ma daeawtukum 'ilyh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa nushi w'irshady lakum 'aya jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,144,"'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum salh: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allh, ftufridwnh balebad? 'iiniy mrsal min allah 'ilykm, hafiz ealaa hadhih alrisalat kama tlqytha ean allh, fahdharuu eqabh teala, wamtthlu ma daeawtukum 'ilyh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa nushi w'irshady lakum 'aya jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,145,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum salh: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allh, ftufridwnh balebad? 'iiniy mrsal min allah 'ilykm, hafiz ealaa hadhih alrisalat kama tlqytha ean allh, fahdharuu eqabh teala, wamtthlu ma daeawtukum 'ilyh. wama 'atlub minkum ealaa nushi w'irshady lakum 'aya jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,146,"aytrkkm rabukum fima 'antum fih min alnaeim mstqryn fi hadhih aldunya aminin min aleadhab walzwal walmwt? fi hadayiq mthmrt waeuyun jariat wazurue kathirat wanakhl thmrha yane lyn ndyj, watanhitun min aljibal bywtana mahryn bnhtha, 'ashiryn batiryn"
  26,147,"aytrkkm rabukum fima 'antum fih min alnaeim mstqryn fi hadhih aldunya aminin min aleadhab walzwal walmwt? fi hadayiq mthmrt waeuyun jariat wazurue kathirat wanakhl thmrha yane lyn ndyj, watanhitun min aljibal bywtana mahryn bnhtha, 'ashiryn batiryn"
  26,148,"aytrkkm rabukum fima 'antum fih min alnaeim mstqryn fi hadhih aldunya aminin min aleadhab walzwal walmwt? fi hadayiq mthmrt waeuyun jariat wazurue kathirat wanakhl thmrha yane lyn ndyj, watanhitun min aljibal bywtana mahryn bnhtha, 'ashiryn batiryn"
  26,149,"aytrkkm rabukum fima 'antum fih min alnaeim mstqryn fi hadhih aldunya aminin min aleadhab walzwal walmwt? fi hadayiq mthmrt waeuyun jariat wazurue kathirat wanakhl thmrha yane lyn ndyj, watanhitun min aljibal bywtana mahryn bnhtha, 'ashiryn batiryn"
  26,150,"fkhafu euqubat allh, wa'aqbaluu nshy, wala tnqadu li'amr almusrifin ealaa 'anfusahum almtmadyn fi mesyt allah aladhin dabu ealaa al'ifsad fi al'ard 'ifsadana la 'iislah fyh"
  26,151,"fkhafu euqubat allh, wa'aqbaluu nshy, wala tnqadu li'amr almusrifin ealaa 'anfusahum almtmadyn fi mesyt allah aladhin dabu ealaa al'ifsad fi al'ard 'ifsadana la 'iislah fyh"
  26,152,"fkhafu euqubat allh, wa'aqbaluu nshy, wala tnqadu li'amr almusrifin ealaa 'anfusahum almtmadyn fi mesyt allah aladhin dabu ealaa al'ifsad fi al'ard 'ifsadana la 'iislah fyh"
  26,153,"qalt thamud lnbyha salh: ma 'ant 'iilaa min aladhin suhru sihrana kthyrana, hataa ghalab alsihr ealaa eqlk. ma 'ant 'iilaa fard mumathil lana fi albashariat min bani adm, fkyf ttmyz ealayna balrsal? fat bihujat wadihatan tadulu ealaa thubut rsaltk, 'iin kunt sadqana fi dewak 'ana allah arslk 'ilyna"
  26,154,"qalt thamud lnbyha salh: ma 'ant 'iilaa min aladhin suhru sihrana kthyrana, hataa ghalab alsihr ealaa eqlk. ma 'ant 'iilaa fard mumathil lana fi albashariat min bani adm, fkyf ttmyz ealayna balrsal? fat bihujat wadihatan tadulu ealaa thubut rsaltk, 'iin kunt sadqana fi dewak 'ana allah arslk 'ilyna"
  26,155,"qal lahum salh- waqad 'atahum bnaqt akhrjha allah lah min alskhrt-: hadhih naqat allah laha nasib min alma' fi yawm melwm, walakum nasib minh fi yawm akhr. lays lakum 'ana tshrbu fi alyawm aldhy hu nsybha, wala hi tshrb fi alyawm aldhy hu nsybkm, wala tnalwha bishay' mimaa ysw'ha kdarb 'aw qutil 'aw nahw dhlk, fyhlkkm allah bedhab ywm tezm shdth; bsbb ma yaqae fih min alhwl walshdt"
  26,156,"qal lahum salh- waqad 'atahum bnaqt akhrjha allah lah min alskhrt-: hadhih naqat allah laha nasib min alma' fi yawm melwm, walakum nasib minh fi yawm akhr. lays lakum 'ana tshrbu fi alyawm aldhy hu nsybha, wala hi tshrb fi alyawm aldhy hu nsybkm, wala tnalwha bishay' mimaa ysw'ha kdarb 'aw qutil 'aw nahw dhlk, fyhlkkm allah bedhab ywm tezm shdth; bsbb ma yaqae fih min alhwl walshdt"
  26,157,"fnhru alnaqt, fa'asbahuu mthsryn ealaa ma faealuu lamma ayqnu baledhab, falam yanfaeuhum ndmhm"
  26,158,"fnzl bihim eadhab allah aladhi twedhm bih salih ealayh alslam, fahlkhm. 'iina fi 'ihlak thamud laebrt liman aietabar bhdha almsyr, wama kan 'aktharuhum mwmnyn"
  26,159,"w'in rabak lahu aleaziz alqahir almntqm min aedayh almkdhbyn, alrahim biman aman min khlqh"
  26,160,"kadhdhabt qawm lut brsalth, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lsayr rusul allh; li'ana ma jawu bih min altwhyd waswl alshraye wahd"
  26,161,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,162,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,163,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,164,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,165,"atnkhwn aldhukur min bani adm, wttrkwn ma khalaq allah lastmtaekm wtnaslkm min azwajkm? bal 'antum qawm - bhdhh almesyt- mtjawzwn ma abahh allah lakum min alhlal 'iilaa alhram"
  26,166,"atnkhwn aldhukur min bani adm, wttrkwn ma khalaq allah lastmtaekm wtnaslkm min azwajkm? bal 'antum qawm - bhdhh almesyt- mtjawzwn ma abahh allah lakum min alhlal 'iilaa alhram"
  26,167,"qal qawm lwt: layin lam ttrk ya lut nahyana ean 'ityan aldhukur wtqbyh felh, latakunana min almtrwdyn min bladna"
  26,168,"qal lut lhm: 'iiniy liemlkm aldhy temlwnh min 'ityan aldhkwr, lamn almbghdyn lah bghdana shdydana"
  26,169,"thm daea lut rabih hinama yayis min astjabthm lah qayla rbb anqdhny wa'anqadh 'ahli mimaa yemlh qawmi min hadhih almesyt alqbyht, wmin eqwbtk alty stsybhm"
  26,170,"fnjynah wa'ahl baytih walmstjybyn ldewth 'ajmaein 'iilaa ejwzana min ahlh, wahi amrath, lm tsharkhm fi al'iyman, fkant min albaqin fi aleadhab walhlak"
  26,171,"fnjynah wa'ahl baytih walmstjybyn ldewth 'ajmaein 'iilaa ejwzana min ahlh, wahi amrath, lm tsharkhm fi al'iyman, fkant min albaqin fi aleadhab walhlak"
  26,172,"thm 'ahlakna man edahm min alkafarat ashdd 'ihlak, wa'anzalna ealayhim hijaratan min alsama' kalmtr ahlkthm, fqabuh mtr min 'andharahum rusuluhum walam yastajibuu lhm; faqad 'unzl bihim ashdd 'anwae alhlak waltdmyr"
  26,173,"thm 'ahlakna man edahm min alkafarat ashdd 'ihlak, wa'anzalna ealayhim hijaratan min alsama' kalmtr ahlkthm, fqabuh mtr min 'andharahum rusuluhum walam yastajibuu lhm; faqad 'unzl bihim ashdd 'anwae alhlak waltdmyr"
  26,174,"'in fi dhalik aleiqab aladhi nazal biqawm lut laebrt wmwezt, ytez biha almkdhbwn. wama kan 'aktharuhum mwmnyn"
  26,175,"w'in rabak lahu aleaziz alghalb aldhy yqhr almkdhbyn, alrahim bieibadih almwmnyn"
  26,176,"kdhdhab 'ashab al'ard dhat alshajar almltf rasuluhum sheybana fi rsalth, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsalat. 'iidh qal lahum sheyb: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allah ealaa shrkkm wmeasykm? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum min allah lhdaytkm, hafiz ealaa ma awha allah bih 'ily min alrsalt, fkhafu eiqab allh, watabaeuu ma daeawtukum 'iilayh min hdayt allh; ltrshdu, wama 'atlub minkum ealaa dueayiy lakum 'iilaa al'iiman biallah ay jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,177,"kdhdhab 'ashab al'ard dhat alshajar almltf rasuluhum sheybana fi rsalth, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsalat. 'iidh qal lahum sheyb: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allah ealaa shrkkm wmeasykm? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum min allah lhdaytkm, hafiz ealaa ma awha allah bih 'ily min alrsalt, fkhafu eiqab allh, watabaeuu ma daeawtukum 'iilayh min hdayt allh; ltrshdu, wama 'atlub minkum ealaa dueayiy lakum 'iilaa al'iiman biallah ay jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,178,"kdhdhab 'ashab al'ard dhat alshajar almltf rasuluhum sheybana fi rsalth, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsalat. 'iidh qal lahum sheyb: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allah ealaa shrkkm wmeasykm? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum min allah lhdaytkm, hafiz ealaa ma awha allah bih 'ily min alrsalt, fkhafu eiqab allh, watabaeuu ma daeawtukum 'iilayh min hdayt allh; ltrshdu, wama 'atlub minkum ealaa dueayiy lakum 'iilaa al'iiman biallah ay jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,179,"kdhdhab 'ashab al'ard dhat alshajar almltf rasuluhum sheybana fi rsalth, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsalat. 'iidh qal lahum sheyb: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allah ealaa shrkkm wmeasykm? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum min allah lhdaytkm, hafiz ealaa ma awha allah bih 'ily min alrsalt, fkhafu eiqab allh, watabaeuu ma daeawtukum 'iilayh min hdayt allh; ltrshdu, wama 'atlub minkum ealaa dueayiy lakum 'iilaa al'iiman biallah ay jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,180,"kdhdhab 'ashab al'ard dhat alshajar almltf rasuluhum sheybana fi rsalth, fakanuu bhdha mkdhdhibyn lajamie alrsalat. 'iidh qal lahum sheyb: 'alaa takhshawn eiqab allah ealaa shrkkm wmeasykm? 'iiniy mrsal 'iilaykum min allah lhdaytkm, hafiz ealaa ma awha allah bih 'ily min alrsalt, fkhafu eiqab allh, watabaeuu ma daeawtukum 'iilayh min hdayt allh; ltrshdu, wama 'atlub minkum ealaa dueayiy lakum 'iilaa al'iiman biallah ay jza', ma jzayy 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"